<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>수학원정대 중등 여름학기 준비</title>
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700;900&display=swap');
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --bg:   #0F0A1E;
  --bg2:  #1A0F35;
  --p1:   #7C3AED;
  --p2:   #9B5CF6;
  --p3:   #C4A8FF;
  --pp:   rgba(124,58,237,.15);
  --y1:   #F5C518;
  --y2:   rgba(245,197,24,.12);
  --r1:   #FF4D4D;
  --r2:   rgba(255,77,77,.12);
  --g1:   #10D5C2;
  --g2:   rgba(16,213,194,.10);
  --o1:   #FF8C42;
  --o2:   rgba(255,140,66,.12);
  --wh:   #FFFFFF;
  --w80:  rgba(255,255,255,.80);
  --w60:  rgba(255,255,255,.60);
  --w40:  rgba(255,255,255,.40);
  --w15:  rgba(255,255,255,.10);
  --bd:   rgba(255,255,255,.10);
}
body{
  font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;
  background:var(--bg);
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;
  padding:0;gap:0;
}

/* ── 카드 공통 ── */
.card{
  width:100%;max-width:680px;
  background:linear-gradient(155deg,var(--bg2) 0%,var(--bg) 100%);
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--bd);
}
.card::before{
  content:'';position:absolute;
  width:500px;height:500px;border-radius:50%;
  top:-160px;right:-160px;pointer-events:none;
  background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(255,140,66,.16) 0%,transparent 65%);
}
.inner{position:relative;z-index:1;padding:48px 44px 52px}

.num{
  position:absolute;top:20px;right:20px;z-index:2;
  font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;
  padding:5px 12px;border-radius:20px;border:1px solid var(--bd);
  color:var(--o1);background:rgba(255,140,66,.15);
}
.eyebrow{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:10px;color:var(--o1)}
.card-title{font-size:clamp(21px,4vw,27px);font-weight:900;color:var(--wh);line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:24px}
.yl{color:var(--y1)} .rd{color:var(--r1)} .or{color:var(--o1)} .gn{color:var(--g1)}

/* 박스 */
.ibox{border-radius:12px;padding:16px 20px;margin-top:16px;font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:var(--w80)}
.ib-o{background:var(--o2);border:1px solid rgba(255,140,66,.25)}
.ib-p{background:var(--pp);border:1px solid rgba(124,58,237,.25)}
.ib-r{background:var(--r2);border:1px solid rgba(255,77,77,.25)}
.ib-y{background:var(--y2);border:1px solid rgba(245,197,24,.25)}
.ib-g{background:var(--g2);border:1px solid rgba(16,213,194,.25)}
.ibox b{color:var(--y1)}
.ibox .ob{color:var(--o1);font-weight:700}
.ibox .rb{color:var(--r1);font-weight:700}
.ibox .gb{color:var(--g1);font-weight:700}
.src{font-size:11px;color:var(--w40);text-align:right;margin-top:8px}

/* 배지 */
.badge-y{background:var(--y1);color:#0F0A1E;font-size:12px;font-weight:900;padding:7px 16px;border-radius:20px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.badge-r{background:var(--r1);color:#fff;font-size:9px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:7px;margin-left:5px;vertical-align:middle}

/* 3열 게이지 */
.g3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px}
.gi{text-align:center}
.gc{width:82px;height:82px;border-radius:50%;margin:0 auto 10px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.gp{font-size:20px;font-weight:900;line-height:1}
.gl{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;margin-top:3px}
.gc-p{background:rgba(124,58,237,.2);border:2px solid rgba(124,58,237,.4)}.gc-p .gp,.gc-p .gl{color:var(--p3)}
.gc-o{background:rgba(255,140,66,.15);border:2px solid rgba(255,140,66,.35)}.gc-o .gp,.gc-o .gl{color:var(--o1)}
.gc-r{background:rgba(255,77,77,.15);border:2px solid rgba(255,77,77,.35)}.gc-r .gp,.gc-r .gl{color:var(--r1)}
.g-grade{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--wh);margin-bottom:3px}
.g-note{font-size:11px;color:var(--w40);line-height:1.5}

/* 악순환 */
.cycle-box{background:rgba(255,77,77,.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,77,77,.2);border-radius:16px;padding:22px 20px;margin:18px 0;text-align:center}
.cycle-title{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--r1);margin-bottom:14px;letter-spacing:.04em}
.cy-items{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;align-items:center}
.cy-i{background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:9px;padding:9px 18px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--w80);width:82%}
.cy-arr{font-size:16px;color:var(--r1);padding:3px 0}
.cy-end{background:rgba(255,77,77,.15);border:1px solid rgba(255,77,77,.3);border-radius:9px;padding:9px 18px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--r1);width:82%}

/* 2열 비교 */
.two-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;margin-bottom:18px}
.tg-i{border-radius:14px;padding:16px 14px}
.tg-g{background:rgba(16,213,194,.07);border:1px solid rgba(16,213,194,.22)}
.tg-b{background:rgba(255,77,77,.07);border:1px solid rgba(255,77,77,.22)}
.tg-icon{font-size:18px;margin-bottom:6px}
.tg-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:7px}
.tg-g .tg-title{color:var(--g1)}.tg-b .tg-title{color:var(--r1)}
.tg-list{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px}
.tg-list li{font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;color:var(--w60);padding-left:13px;position:relative}
.tg-g .tg-list li::before{content:"✓";position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--g1);font-size:11px}
.tg-b .tg-list li::before{content:"✗";position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--r1);font-size:11px}

/* ── 학교별 시험 섹션 ── */
.school-section{margin:0 0 20px}
.school-legend{display:flex;gap:14px;margin-bottom:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.leg-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:11px;color:var(--w60)}
.leg-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%}

.school-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse}
.school-table th{
  padding:10px 12px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;
  text-align:left;border-bottom:1px solid var(--bd);
}
.th-name{color:var(--o1);width:60px}
.th-date{color:var(--w60);width:90px}
.th-track{color:var(--w60)}

.school-table td{
  padding:11px 12px;font-size:12px;color:var(--w80);
  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);
  vertical-align:top;line-height:1.55;
}
.school-table tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none}
.school-table tr:hover td{background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)}

.td-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:700}
.td-date{font-size:12px;color:var(--w40);white-space:nowrap}

/* 학교 색상 */
.s-geum{color:#FF8C42}
.s-daek{color:#A78BFA}
.s-jang{color:#10D5C2}
.s-ok{color:#F5C518}
.s-jangw{color:#60A5FA}
.s-deok{color:#F472B6}

/* 트랙 태그 */
.track-tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:5px;margin-top:5px}
.ttag{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px}
.tt-r{background:rgba(255,77,77,.15);color:var(--r1);border:1px solid rgba(255,77,77,.2)}
.tt-o{background:rgba(255,140,66,.12);color:var(--o1);border:1px solid rgba(255,140,66,.2)}
.tt-g{background:rgba(16,213,194,.1);color:var(--g1);border:1px solid rgba(16,213,194,.2)}
.tt-p{background:rgba(124,58,237,.15);color:var(--p3);border:1px solid rgba(124,58,237,.2)}
.tt-y{background:rgba(245,197,24,.1);color:var(--y1);border:1px solid rgba(245,197,24,.2)}

/* D-day 뱃지 */
.dday{
  display:inline-block;font-size:10px;font-weight:900;
  padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;
  margin-left:4px;vertical-align:middle;
}
.dd-soon{background:rgba(255,77,77,.2);color:var(--r1);border:1px solid rgba(255,77,77,.3)}
.dd-prep{background:rgba(245,197,24,.15);color:var(--y1);border:1px solid rgba(245,197,24,.25)}
.dd-ok{background:rgba(16,213,194,.1);color:var(--g1);border:1px solid rgba(16,213,194,.2)}

/* 첨삭 섹션 */
.test-section{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;margin:18px 0}
.test-item{background:var(--w15);border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:14px;padding:18px 20px;display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start}
.test-icon{width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:20px;flex-shrink:0}
.ti-o{background:rgba(255,140,66,.2)}
.ti-p{background:rgba(124,58,237,.2)}
.ti-g{background:rgba(16,213,194,.15)}
.test-name{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:5px}
.tn-o{color:var(--o1)}.tn-p{color:var(--p3)}.tn-g{color:var(--g1)}
.test-desc{font-size:12px;line-height:1.65;color:var(--w60)}
.test-tag{display:inline-block;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 9px;border-radius:7px;margin-top:6px;background:rgba(255,140,66,.15);border:1px solid rgba(255,140,66,.3);color:var(--o1)}

/* 비교 테이블 */
.vs-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:12px 0}
.vs-table .vs-hdr{background:transparent}
.vs-table .vs-hdr th{
  padding:9px 12px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--bd);text-align:center;
}
.vs-table .vs-hdr th:first-child{text-align:left}
.vs-table .vs-hdr .vth-w{color:var(--o1)}
.vs-table .vs-hdr .vth-l{color:var(--w40)}
.vs-table td{padding:11px 12px;font-size:12px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);color:var(--w80)}
.vs-table td:first-child{color:var(--w60)}
.vs-table td:nth-child(2){text-align:center;color:var(--y1);font-size:16px}
.vs-table td:nth-child(3){text-align:center;color:rgba(255,255,255,.2);font-size:16px}
.vs-table tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none}

/* CTA */
.cta-full{
  background:var(--y1);border-radius:16px;
  padding:28px 28px;text-align:center;margin-top:8px;
}
.cta-title{font-size:17px;font-weight:900;color:#0F0A1E;margin-bottom:6px}
.cta-sub{font-size:13px;color:rgba(15,10,30,.65);line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:22px}
.cta-btn-wrap{display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
.cta-btn-main{
  background:#0F0A1E;color:var(--y1);
  font-size:14px;font-weight:900;
  padding:14px 28px;border-radius:12px;
  text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;
}
.cta-btn-sub{
  background:rgba(15,10,30,.12);color:#0F0A1E;
  font-size:13px;font-weight:700;
  padding:14px 22px;border-radius:12px;
  text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;
  border:1px solid rgba(15,10,30,.15);
}
.cta-tel{font-size:13px;color:rgba(15,10,30,.5);margin-top:14px}

/* 구분선 */
.section-div{width:100%;max-width:680px;height:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--o1),var(--p1));opacity:.4}

@media(max-width:500px){
  .inner{padding:36px 22px 42px}
  .two-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .g3{gap:8px}.gc{width:70px;height:70px}.gp{font-size:17px}
  .cta-btn-wrap{flex-direction:column}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ══ 카드 1 표지 ══ -->
<div class="card">
<span class="num">01 / 07</span>
<div class="inner">
  <p class="eyebrow">📊 수학원정대 중등부 · 2026 리포트</p>
  <h1 class="card-title">학원을 다니는데<br><span class="yl">왜 수학이 안 오를까요</span></h1>
  <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;color:var(--w60);margin-bottom:32px">
    사교육 참여율 64.7%인데 중3 수포자는 32.9%입니다.<br>
    더 많이 배울수록 더 모르게 되는 이유.<br>
    데이터로 정확하게 짚겠습니다.
  </p>
  <div class="g3">
    <div class="gi">
      <div class="gc gc-p"><div class="gp">64.7%</div><div class="gl">사교육</div></div>
      <div class="g-grade">수학 사교육 참여</div>
      <div class="g-note">10명 중 6명<br>학원·과외 수강</div>
    </div>
    <div class="gi">
      <div class="gc gc-o"><div class="gp">30.3%</div><div class="gl">미이해</div></div>
      <div class="g-grade">선행 미이해율</div>
      <div class="g-note">3명 중 1명<br>"이해 안 됨"</div>
    </div>
    <div class="gi">
      <div class="gc gc-r"><div class="gp">14.9%</div><div class="gl">중3미달</div></div>
      <div class="g-grade">2025 최신</div>
      <div class="g-note">전년比 +2.2%p<br>역주행<span class="badge-r">최신</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:8px">
    <span class="badge-y">📋 교육부 2025.6.24 · 사교육걱정없는세상 2025.11 기반</span>
    <span style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--w40)">수학원정대</span>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- ══ 카드 2 사교육 역설 ══ -->
<div class="card">
<span class="num">02 / 07</span>
<div class="inner">
  <p class="eyebrow">DATA 01 · 사교육 역설</p>
  <h2 class="card-title">이해 없는 선행이<br><span class="rd">수포자를 만드는 과정</span></h2>

  <div class="two-grid">
    <div class="tg-i tg-g">
      <div class="tg-icon">✅</div>
      <div class="tg-title">효과 있는 수업</div>
      <ul class="tg-list">
        <li>현행 완성 후 다음 단원</li>
        <li>개념을 말로 설명 가능</li>
        <li>풀이 과정 서술 훈련</li>
        <li>오답 원인 분석 루틴</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="tg-i tg-b">
      <div class="tg-icon">❌</div>
      <div class="tg-title">역효과 수업</div>
      <ul class="tg-list">
        <li>이해 전 진도만 빠름</li>
        <li>답은 맞지만 이유 모름</li>
        <li>시험 전 벼락치기 반복</li>
        <li>다음 단원 가면 까먹음</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="cycle-box">
    <div class="cycle-title">⚠ 이해 없는 선행의 악순환</div>
    <div class="cy-items">
      <div class="cy-i">현행 미완 상태에서 선행 시작</div>
      <div class="cy-arr">↓</div>
      <div class="cy-i">진도는 나가지만 이해 안 됨</div>
      <div class="cy-arr">↓</div>
      <div class="cy-i">시험 직전 벼락치기 반복</div>
      <div class="cy-arr">↓</div>
      <div class="cy-i">점수는 나오지만 실력 없음</div>
      <div class="cy-arr">↓</div>
      <div class="cy-end">더 어려운 단원에서 완전히 막힘 → 수포자</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ibox ib-o">
    교사가 꼽은 수포자 원인 1위:<br>
    <span class="ob">"누적된 학습 결손 (44.6%)"</span><br>
    학생은 문제가 어렵다고 느끼지만 실제 원인은 기초 결손입니다.
  </div>
  <p class="src">출처: 사교육걱정없는세상 전국 수학교육 인식 설문 (2025.11, n=6,652)</p>
</div>
</div>

<!-- ══ 카드 3 학교별 시험 섹션 ══ -->
<div class="card">
<span class="num">03 / 07</span>
<div class="inner">
  <p class="eyebrow">🏫 근처 학교 · 2학기 시험 일정</p>
  <h2 class="card-title">중1 첫 2학기 시험<br><span class="yl">학교별 집중 관리트랙</span></h2>

  <div class="school-section">
    <table class="school-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th class="th-name">학교</th>
          <th class="th-date">시험일</th>
          <th class="th-track">4주 챌린지 학교별 운영</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td class="td-name s-geum">금호중</td>
          <td class="td-date">10/22~10/23</td>
          <td>
            신설교 기출 없음 → 4주차 예상 출제 유형 분석지 자체 제작
            <div class="track-tags">
              <span class="ttag tt-r">기출 없음</span>
              <span class="ttag tt-o">유형분석 자체제작</span>
              <span class="ttag tt-g">진도프린트 수집</span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="td-name s-daek">대경중</td>
          <td class="td-date">9/30~10/2</td>
          <td>
            기출 보유 → 4주 내 기출 유형 다회독 수준별 학습 / 심화형 집중
            <div class="track-tags">
              <span class="ttag tt-p">기출 다회독</span>
              <span class="ttag tt-o">수준별 학습</span>
              <span class="ttag tt-r">심화 집중</span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="td-name s-jang">장충중</td>
          <td class="td-date">10/8~10/13</td>
          <td>
            남학생 비율 고려 → 미니테스트 타이머 경쟁 방식 / 숙제 완료율·집중도 관리
            <div class="track-tags">
              <span class="ttag tt-g">타이머 경쟁</span>
              <span class="ttag tt-o">숙제 완료율 관리</span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="td-name s-ok">옥정중</td>
          <td class="td-date">9/22~9/23</td>
          <td>
            가장 빠른 시험 → 4주차부터 내신 모드 병행 / 입체도형보다 평면까지 완성 후 전환
            <div class="track-tags">
              <span class="ttag tt-r">가장 빠름</span>
              <span class="ttag tt-y">내신 모드 병행</span>
              <span class="ttag tt-p">단원 완성 후 전환</span>
            </div>
          </td>
